SowGrow eliminates the need for expensive fertilizers that contain harmful chemicals.  
Users can enjoy the fruits of their labor knowing that their soil is rich in nutrients
 and sustainable. 




SowGrow offers unique individual characteristics that will attract consumers:

 Organic-Provides a soil supplement with no added chemicals


   Nutrient Aiding-Give plants extra nutrients for increased growth and development


   Versatility-Can be applied to any plant or crop


   Easy to Use-Simplifies application and use of product


   Environmentally Friendly-Contributes to the green initiave in reducing carbon footprint



Statement


Organic Roots striveMission s to create sustainable, organic, and environmentally friendly soil and farming supplements.   By providing environmentally safe and beneficial products, we look to create a positive earth friendly trend for customers to follow.

Vision Statement


The vision of Organic Roots is to lead the biochar market and research the possibilities of other environmentally safe and sustainable soil supplements.

Benefit
Provides a soil supplement with no added chemicals.
Gives plants extra nutrients for increased growth and development.
Can be applied to any plant or crop.
Simple application and use.
Contributes to the green initiative by reducing carbon footprint.



